Video footage shared on social media shows Ukrainian forces finding the tank. Ukrainian forces who previously captured a tank of the same type said it its systems make it "exceptional adding that it is "good to drive", "fast, manoeuvrable" and "comes and goes quickly". It comes after NATO Secretary-General Jens Stoltenberg warned that a war between Russia and NATO would be "much worse" than the situation in Ukraine. He said it is "the most dangerous situation in Europe since World War Two". FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES...